      "source": [
        "這組數據展示了五位玩家 (yoyo, yll, wizza, k3x, bug) 在遊戲中的得分情況。\n",

        "yll 和 k3x 的得分處於中等水平，分別為 31 分和 32 分。\n",

        "最高分為 52 分，最低分為 20 分。\n",
        "分數差距較大，說明玩家之間的遊戲水平存在差異。\n",
        "結論:\n",
        "\n",
        "這組數據和圖表提供了一個關於五位玩家遊戲表現的概覽。 可以看出，bug 在遊戲中表現最佳，而 yoyo 的得分最低。 後續可以根據這些信息進行更深入的分析，例如研究不同玩家得分差異的原因，或者分析玩家遊戲水平的變化趨勢。"
      ],

    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "source": [
        "import pandas as pd\n",
        "\n",
        "# 玩家姓名、積分和策略\n",
        "players = ['yoyo', 'yll', 'wizza', 'k3x', 'bug']\n",
        "scores = [20, 31, 49, 32, 52]\n",
        "strategies = []\n",
        "\n",
        "# 根據邏輯判斷策略\n",
        "for player in players:\n",
        "    if player in ['k3x', 'bug']:\n",
        "            strategies.append('A')  # k3x 和 bug 為策略 A\n",
        "    else:\n",
        "     strategies.append('B')  # 其他玩家為策略 B\n",
        "\n",
        "              # 使用 pandas 建立 DataFrame\n",
        "\n",
        "data = {'玩家 (Player)': players, '積分 (Score)': scores, '策略 (Strategy)': strategies}\n",
        "df = pd.DataFrame(data)\n",
        "\n",
        "                        # 顯示表格\n",
        "print(df)"
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "colab": {
          "base_uri": "https://localhost:8080/"
        },
        "id": "pCTJTbEU0ywG",
        "outputId": "ee098e58-771d-4d9f-b6dd-fa2ed51710fb"
      },
      "execution_count": 25,
      "outputs": [
        {
          "output_type": "stream",
          "name": "stdout",
          "text": [
            "  玩家 (Player)  積分 (Score) 策略 (Strategy)\n",
            "0        yoyo          20             B\n",
            "1         yll          31             B\n",
            "2       wizza          49             B\n",
            "3         k3x          32             A\n",
            "4         bug          52             A\n"
          ]
        }
      ]

    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "source": [
        "!pip install scipy\n",
        "import pandas as pd\n",
        "from scipy import stats\n",
        "\n",
        "# Assuming 'df' is your DataFrame\n",
        "\n",
        "# Convert '策略 (Strategy)' to numerical representation (0 for B, 1 for A)\n",
        "df['Strategy_Numeric'] = df['策略 (Strategy)'].map({'B': 0, 'A': 1})\n",
        "\n",
        "# Calculate point-biserial correlation\n",
        "correlation, p_value = stats.pointbiserialr(df['Strategy_Numeric'], df['積分 (Score)'])\n",
        "\n",
        "print(f\"Point-Biserial Correlation: {correlation}\")\n",
        "print(f\"P-value: {p_value}\")\n",
        "\n",
        "# Interpretation:\n",
        "if p_value < 0.05:\n",
        "    print(\"There is a statistically significant correlation between strategy and score.\")\n",
        "    if correlation > 0:\n",
        "     print(\"Strategy A tends to be associated with higher scores.\")\n",
        "    else:\n",
        "     print(\"Strategy A tends to be associated with lower scores.\")\n",
        "else:\n",
        "    print(\"There is no statistically significant correlation between strategy and score.\")"
      ],
